### WTDU API Smoke Tests
# Run these in VS Code REST Client or similar

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### 1. Parse natural language text
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/parse
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "morgen 8 uhr zahnarzt",
  "timezone": "Europe/Berlin"
}

### 2. Create reminder
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reminders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Demo Reminder",
  "note": "This is a test reminder",
  "dueAt": "2024-01-20T10:00:00.000Z",
  "timezone": "Europe/Berlin"
}

### 3. Get all pending reminders
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reminders

### 4. Register device token for push
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/push/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "platform": "ios",
  "token": "ExponentPushToken[test-token]"
}

### 5. Manual send (replace REMINDER_ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reminders/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "REMINDER_ID"
}

### 6. Snooze reminder (replace REMINDER_ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reminders/REMINDER_ID/snooze

### 7. Mark reminder as done (replace REMINDER_ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reminders/REMINDER_ID/done

